title: 2016 Rip Curl GromSearch presented by Banzai Bowls | Event #2 - Banzai Bowls Maneuver of the Event
description:
The 2016 Rip Curl GromSearch presented by Banzai Bowls - Event #2 Kewalos, HI. 
The Banzai Bowls Maneuver of the Event was earned by Cole Alves who earned $300 courtesy of Banzai Bowls for this tail high rotation. 

Video: Willi Edwards
